name: VacationFinder
0:
”Alexa, ask Vacation Finder where should I go”
”Alexa, ask Vacation Finder what country should I visit”
”Alexa, ask Vacation Finder where should I go on vacation”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: vacation finder
des: A skill to choose a random country to visit on vacation. Not sure where to go this year? Ask Alexa "where should I go" (or variances) and she'll choose you a random vacation destination.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
